snippet.title: Arkanoid - BBC Micro [Longplay]
snippet.description:
What do you think of Arkanoid?
This is a longplay of the BBC Micro version which was released in 1987.
The video will show a full walkthrough and display the gameplay.

Did you play this game or have any opinion on what you can see?
Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

Developed by:  Imagine, Hit Squad
